title: Episode #51 - John Tague, ME, & a little LeeAnn
description: Past Bertcast guest, friend, actor, writer, & producer John Tague hangs out in the Mancave during the Alabama vs. Auburn game and talks about his Karate Black Belt, our space shuttle play, his new Indiegogo project, and my fears of Burning Man.
